<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="javascripts/sign_up.js"></script>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>sign_up</title>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- 공백사용금지 :   <input type="text" name="test" id="test" onkeyup="noSpaceForm(this);" onchange="noSpaceForm(this);" /> -->
    <h1 id="sign_up_h1">
        회원가입&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp</h1>
    <div class="sign_up_form">
        <form action="user2/sign_up_process" id="form_all" method="post" onsubmit="return submitCheck()">
            <label>아이디</label>
            <p><input type = "id" name="id" id="id" onkeyup="noSpaceForm(this)" required>
            </p>
            <br id="id_form_check_br" />
            <p id="id_form_guide" style="display:none; color:red; font-size: 8px;">8~20자 영문대문자, 영문소문자, 숫자, 특수문자를 모두
                사용해야합니다.</p>


            <p>비밀번호</p>
            <p><input type="password" name="password" id="pw" style="ime-mode:inactive" onkeyup="noSpaceForm(this)"
                    required></p>
            <br id="pw_form_check_br" />
            <p id="pw_form_guide"></p>


            <p>비밀번호 확인</p>
            <p><input type="password" name="password_check" id="pw2" style="ime-mode:inactive"
                    onkeyup="noSpaceForm(this)" required></p>
            <br id="pw2_form_check_br" />
            <p id="pw2_form_guide"></p>

            <p>닉네임</p>
            <p><input type="text" name="nickname" id="nickname" onkeyup="noSpaceForm(this)" required></p>
            <br id="nickname_form_check_br" />
            <p id="nickname_form_guide"></p>

            <p>전화번호( - 없이 입력)</p>
            <p><input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" onkeyup="noSpaceForm(this)" required></p>
            <br id="phone_form_check_br" />
            <p id="phone_form_guide"></p>

            <p>지역</p>
            <p><input type="text" id="area" name="area" required></p>
            <br id="area_form_check_br" />
            <p id="area_form_guide"></p>

            <p>성별</p>
            <div style="border: 1px solid gray; width : 173px;  ">
                <input type="radio" id="man" name="gender" value="male" required />
                <label for="man">남성</label>
                <input type="radio" id="woman" name="gender" value="female" />
                <label for="woman">여성</label>
            </div>

            <br />
            <br />
            <br />
            <input id="sign_up_submit" type="submit" value="회원 가입 신청">
            </p>
        </form>

    </div>
    <div>

    </div>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0 auto;
            align-content: center;
        }

        #sign_up_h1 {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .sign_up_form {
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 40%;
        }

        #sign_up_submit {
            background: rgb(0, 118, 255);
            color: white;
            width: 173px;
            height: 50px;
            font-size: 20px;
            border-radius: 7px 7px 7px 7px;
        }
    </style>
</body>

</html>